articlegeek.com
Each article has an URL and a link to /scripts/publish.php
Open that link and send the header:
Referer: original-article-url

The response is nicely formatted for our purpose:
1. discard everything up to the line containing «name='ArticleTEXT'»
2. the next line is the title
3. the next line is the author (By: author name)
4. the following lines are the article
5. discard everything from the line containing </textarea>
